headline: Deere (DE): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: Deere has followed the market’s trajectory closely, rising in tandem with the S&P 500 over the past six months. The stock has climbed by 10.9% to $423.23 per share while the index has gained 6.1%.
